headline: Stanley Black & Decker Set to Report Q4 Earnings: Is a Beat in Store?
summary: SWK's Q4 2024 results are likely to benefit from strength in the aerospace market. However, weakness in the Industrial and Tools & Outdoor segments is likely to have weighed on its performance.
